{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1468241, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这样就可以增加内卷…", "timestamp": 1618588053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468244, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "迷惑。不是每个人都是能有“创见”的天才。", "timestamp": 1618588061, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468254, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1.感觉还是太难实践，没有人会想吃亏\n2.个人认为有的时候考试真没办法，比如期中期末考，其实都有很大随机性的，有的人考的差也能调分。\n所以cz觉得也没办法把gpa这东西", "timestamp": 1618588126, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "知识不等于考试成绩，但知识也不等于创见", "timestamp": 1618588131, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "迷惑+1 我觉得这样只会让相当多一部分同学彻底失去学习的希望", "timestamp": 1618588171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "创见太主观了", "timestamp": 1618588219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这不是语录吗…", "timestamp": 1618588256, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468290, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你要真有创见就赶紧去解决诺奖难题，何必盯着这几学分难为普通老师和同学呢", "timestamp": 1618588478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468291, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但90也是4.0了呀。", "timestamp": 1618588487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "创见😅😅😅", "timestamp": 1618588520, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468333, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外难道“平平”就代表没学到知识吗？难道普通的努力就要得到比“创见”更低的评价？", "timestamp": 1618588921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1468351, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以前的考试形式都是教授直接面试同学给成绩 参考的是苏联的方式 了解一下", "timestamp": 1618589124, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1469493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 288049, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 同意", "timestamp": 1618628410, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 288049, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "成绩好的同学觉得自己需要学知识，有些学得好的同学GPA却不高。但一方面GPA确实是最简单衡量一个人的指标了。我觉得关键在于改革考试制度。可以出十道题大家讨论，做出十道，但平平的，给九十分，做了三四道，但有创见的，给一百分。这样就可以让知识和成绩统一起来。", "timestamp": 1618587938, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618628407, "url": "", "vote": {}}}